      "raw_text": "DENVER, July 2.-The Western\nFederation of Miners this morning\nreelected Meyer president and Hay\nwood secretary, promising them\nsalaries for the coming year re-\ngardless Of the outcome Of the\nBoise trial. e. c. Mahoney, of\nButte, was reelected acting presi-\ndent.\n\n\nThe convention voted to permit\nHaywood to choose his own repre-\nsentative as secretary during his\nIncarceration."
